data.title: Suara Indonesia Dance
data.content:
Details....
Lashes...
This is called a #suntiang. It is a crown worn by women of the #Minangkabau culture of West Sumatra for festive occasions.
Worn here by @alettafauzi of #suaraindonesiadance for #taripayung performance at a recent #wedding in #Sydney.
